p
  | Hey #{@user.first_name},
p
  | Your project titled 
  em
    = @project.title
  |  has some new contributions:
- if @tasks
  p(style="margin-left: 25px")
    strong
      | New Tasks
    br
    - @tasks.each do |task|
      | - #{task.title}
      br
- if @discussions
  p(style="margin-left: 25px")
    strong
      | New Discussions
    br
    - @discussions.each do |discussion|
      | - #{discussion.title}
      br
p
  | Regards,
p
  | Rails PM Tool